data.description: Welcome to your dream home, with features that today's buyers desire! As you arrive, you'll be captivated by the attractive driveway with mature shade trees, setting the tone for this inviting property. Step onto the spacious front porch, where a cozy porch swing awaits, offering the perfect spot for relaxing evenings.    Inside, the welcoming foyer provides ample space for welcoming guests. This home boasts three well-sized bedrooms and two full bathrooms, ensuring comfort for your family and guests alike. The primary bathroom is a haven of relaxation, complete with a jacuzzi tub perfect for unwinding after a busy day. All window treatments are included, adding convenience and style.    The heart of the home is the kitchen, equipped with modern stainless steel appliances, an abundance of cabinets, and a practical breakfast bar for quick meals. Adjacent to the kitchen, the formal dining room is ideal for hosting dinner parties or enjoying family meals.    Relax in the comfortable living room, featuring a vaulted ceiling that enhances the sense of space. Adjoining the living room is a sunporch, recently renovated, offering a serene retreat to enjoy the outdoors regardless of the weather.     Outdoors, the backyard is partially fenced, providing a safe play area for children or pets, and can be enjoyed from the charming, screened porch.    For your peace of mind, the home includes an ADT security system with a video doorbell camera. Additionally, a whole-house water system located in the garage ensures quality water throughout the home, and a water irrigation system maintains the lawn effortlessly. The recent addition of fresh insulation in the attic enhances the home's energy efficiency.    This home is simply waiting for your personal touches to make it truly your own. Don't miss out on this opportunity-schedule a showing today and come see all the potential this lovely home has to offer!
